534
00:30:50,748 --> 00:30:52,317
Thank you, future President.

535
00:30:52,383 --> 00:30:53,918
Stop that.

536
00:30:53,985 --> 00:30:55,520
It's all thanks to the future President?

537
00:30:55,587 --> 00:30:57,388
You too, Maki?

538
00:30:58,289 --> 00:31:01,492
