544
00:31:20,311 --> 00:31:21,446
The protesters?

545
00:31:21,512 --> 00:31:22,580
No…

546
00:31:25,116 --> 00:31:26,084
Our time capsule.

547
00:31:30,855 --> 00:31:32,824
Let's go there right now.

548
00:31:33,658 --> 00:31:34,993
What?

549
00:31:35,059 --> 00:31:36,194
Let's open it…

550
00:31:37,562 --> 00:31:38,730
The time capsule.

551
00:31:40,765 --> 00:31:41,633
Are you serious?

552
00:31:41,699 --> 00:31:44,068
- Why open it?
- The gun…

553
00:31:45,470 --> 00:31:48,573
Junichi, you're okay with it
since you're a detective?

554
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:49,874
No way,

555
00:31:49,941 --> 00:31:51,676
in fact it'll be even worse for you.

556
00:31:51,743 --> 00:31:55,813
We hid the gun that caused such
a stir back then. If that gets out…

557
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:57,215
Let's go.

558
00:32:01,853 --> 00:32:02,921
Let's go.

559
00:32:08,126 --> 00:32:10,194
Junichi never changes.

560
00:32:12,463 --> 00:32:13,765
Yeah.

561
00:32:15,767 --> 00:32:16,968
Just a little further.

562
00:32:17,035 --> 00:32:18,336
