571
00:32:33,618 --> 00:32:36,187
- Which way do you want to go, Maki?
- Let's do rock, paper, scissors.

572
00:32:36,254 --> 00:32:37,956
Rock, paper, scissors.

573
00:32:38,022 --> 00:32:39,290
Rock, paper, scissors.

574
00:32:39,357 --> 00:32:40,692
