- Me too.

575
00:32:40,758 --> 00:32:41,793
You and me, Naoto.

576
00:32:41,859 --> 00:32:42,694
All right, let's go!

577
00:32:42,760 --> 00:32:44,629
What? Wait for me.

578
00:32:44,696 --> 00:32:45,330
Come on.

579
00:32:45,396 --> 00:32:46,331
- Hurry up, Naoto.
- Wait.

580
00:32:46,397 --> 00:32:47,265
- Naoto.
- Sorry.

581
00:32:47,332 --> 00:32:48,399
Come on, Naoto.

582
00:32:48,466 --> 00:32:49,300
Hurry up.

583
00:32:50,868 --> 00:32:51,703
‪Wow.

584
00:33:17,762 --> 00:33:18,830
Let's go.

585
00:33:30,808 --> 00:33:31,676
- You okay?
- Yeah.

586
00:33:38,683 --> 00:33:40,618
Keisuke. What's wrong?

587
00:33:42,086 --> 00:33:43,154
I don't know…

588
00:33:45,156 --> 00:33:47,992
But I heard

589
00:33:49,527 --> 00:33:51,095
