590
00:33:53,531 --> 00:33:54,665
Wait…

591
00:33:55,967 --> 00:33:58,436
- Where's Naoto?
- He's behind me.

592
00:33:59,904 --> 00:34:01,205
Where's Naoto?

593
00:34:01,272 --> 00:34:02,240
What?

594
00:34:04,342 --> 00:34:06,310
NO TRESPASSING

595
00:34:06,377 --> 00:34:08,246
- Naoto!
- Naoto!

596
00:34:08,312 --> 00:34:10,415
Naoto!

597
00:34:10,481 --> 00:34:11,749
- I'll go look for him.
- Naoto!

598
00:34:11,816 --> 00:34:13,117
I'll go too.

599
00:34:17,321 --> 00:34:18,890
Maki, head back.

600
00:34:18,956 --> 00:34:20,658
Call the police.

601
00:34:21,592 --> 00:34:22,894
By myself?

602
00:34:26,531 --> 00:34:29,267
I'll look for Naoto.
Keisuke, you should go with her.

603
00:34:30,802 --> 00:34:31,869
What?

604
00:34:32,670 --> 00:34:34,072
Take care of Makiko.

605
00:34:38,142 --> 00:34:39,177
Okay.

606
00:34:41,946 --> 00:34:43,214
- Naoto!
- Makiko.

607
00:34:43,815 --> 00:34:45,850
Let's go, Makiko.

608
00:34:46,384 --> 00:34:47,518
Come on, Makiko.

609
00:34:49,120 --> 00:34:50,388
Naoto.

610
00:34:51,556 --> 00:34:52,523
Naoto.

611
00:34:55,860 --> 00:34:57,795
Naoto.

612
00:34:59,931 --> 00:35:00,998
Naoto.

613
00:35:06,170 --> 00:35:07,805
What's the matter? Are you okay?

614
00:35:10,775 --> 00:35:11,976
Can you walk over there?

615
00:35:13,377 --> 00:35:14,245
It's okay.

616
00:35:14,745 --> 00:35:15,947
Take your time.

617
00:35:17,882 --> 00:35:18,850
It's okay.

618
00:35:20,084 --> 00:35:21,519
That's good.

619
00:35:22,086 --> 00:35:25,456
It's okay.

620
00:35:28,025 --> 00:35:29,127
Sit here.

621
00:35:32,230 --> 00:35:33,331
Are you okay?

622
00:35:35,166 --> 00:35:36,100
Yeah.

623
00:35:39,003 --> 00:35:40,304
I'll go check things out.

624
00:35:41,405 --> 00:35:42,640
You stay here.

625
00:35:43,574 --> 00:35:44,709
No, I'll go with you.

626
00:35:46,644 --> 00:35:47,478
It's all right.

627
00:36:12,436 --> 00:36:14,505
Junichi and Naoto are…

628
00:36:15,806 --> 00:36:17,808
Let's hurry and call the police.

629
00:36:18,876 --> 00:36:20,545
We're going to run away?

630
00:36:21,345 --> 00:36:23,848
We're doing this
to save Junichi and Naoto.

631
00:36:27,752 --> 00:36:29,654
Then go by yourself, Keisuke.

632
00:36:30,955 --> 00:36:32,290
Hurry!

633
00:36:48,673 --> 00:36:50,608
- Are you okay?
- Naoto.

634
00:36:51,642 --> 00:36:52,843
Are you okay?

635
00:36:53,644 --> 00:36:54,712
Where's Junichi?

636
00:36:57,615 --> 00:36:58,916
Where's Junichi?

637
00:37:11,996 --> 00:37:12,930
Junichi!

638
00:37:14,665 --> 00:37:17,001
- Is everything all right?
- Junichi.

639
00:37:18,035 --> 00:37:20,871
- What's wrong?
- Where's the police?

640
00:37:20,938 --> 00:37:23,407
- Well…
- Call them right now.

641
00:37:24,141 --> 00:37:25,209
What happened?

642
00:37:26,711 --> 00:37:27,912
You shouldn't go over there.

643
