706
00:44:13,417 --> 00:44:15,586
<i>‪At last, all the players will be present.</i>

707
00:44:15,653 --> 00:44:17,888
<i>‪You're saying that I have an accomplice?</i>

708
00:44:17,955 --> 00:44:19,423
<i>‪"Raise your hand, and I’ll arrest you."</i>

709
00:44:19,490 --> 00:44:21,725
‪-That's what you're saying!
