710
00:44:21,792 --> 00:44:23,994
‪I didn't open the time capsule.

711
00:44:24,061 --> 00:44:25,562
<i>‪Okay.</i>

712
00:44:25,629 --> 00:44:26,730
<i>‪I believe you.</i>

